    {
      "id": "intro_2",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "Of men and galaxies",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 2.87,
      "endTime": 11.19
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_3",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "What is the most influential factor in any human society?",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 11.2,
      "endTime": 18.74,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "What",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "什么"
          },
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_4",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "In man's early days, competition with other creatures must have been critical.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 18.75,
      "endTime": 25.21,
      "analysis": {
        "words": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s1",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "But this phase of our development is now finished.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 25.22,
      "endTime": 28.87,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "This",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "这，这个"
          },
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s2",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "Indeed, we lack practice and experience nowadays in dealing with primitive conditions.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 28.88,
      "endTime": 35.96
    },
    {
      "id": "s3",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "I am sure that, without modern weapons,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 35.97,
      "endTime": 39.2,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s4",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "I would make a very poor show of disputing the ownership of a cave with a bear, and in this I do not think that I stand alone.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 39.21,
      "endTime": 49.64,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Very",
            "pos": "adv.",
            "meaning": "很，非常"
          },
          {
            "word": "This",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "这，这个"
          },
          {
            "word": "Not",
            "pos": "adv.",
            "meaning": "不，不是"
          },
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s5",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "The last creature to compete with man was the mosquito.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 49.65,
      "endTime": 53.95,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Man",
            "pos": "n.",
            "meaning": "男人"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s6",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "But even the mosquito has been subdued by attention to drainage and by chemical sprays.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 53.96,
      "endTime": 61.52
    },
    {
      "id": "s7",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "Competition between ourselves, person against person,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 61.53,
      "endTime": 66.12
    },
    {
      "id": "s8",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "community against community, still persists, however; and it is as fierce as it ever was.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 66.13,
      "endTime": 74.54,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "It",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "它"
          },
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s9",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "But the competition of man against man is not the simple process envisioned in biology.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 74.55,
      "endTime": 81.73,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Man",
            "pos": "n.",
            "meaning": "男人"
          },
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          },
          {
            "word": "Not",
            "pos": "adv.",
            "meaning": "不，不是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s10",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "It is not a simple competition for a fixed amount of food determined by the physical environment,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 81.74,
      "endTime": 88.54,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "It",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "它"
          },
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          },
          {
            "word": "Not",
            "pos": "adv.",
            "meaning": "不，不是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s11",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "because the environment that determines our evolution is no longer essentially physical.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 88.55,
      "endTime": 95.72,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          },
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s12",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "Our environment is chiefly conditoned by the things we believe.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 95.73,
      "endTime": 101.68,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s13",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "Morocco and California are bits of the Earth in very similar latitudes,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 101.69,
      "endTime": 107.46,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Very",
            "pos": "adv.",
            "meaning": "很，非常"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s14",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "both on the west coasts of continents with similar climates, and probably with rather similar natural resources.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 107.47,
      "endTime": 115.78
    },
    {
      "id": "s15",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "Yet their present development is wholly different,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 115.79,
      "endTime": 120.01,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s16",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "not so much because of different people even,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 120.02,
      "endTime": 123.47,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Not",
            "pos": "adv.",
            "meaning": "不，不是"
          },
          {
            "word": "Much",
            "pos": "adv.",
            "meaning": "非常"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s17",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "but because of the different thoughts that exist in the minds of their inhabitants.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 123.48,
      "endTime": 129.44,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s18",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "This is the point I wish to emphasize.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 129.45,
      "endTime": 132.43,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "This",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "这，这个"
          },
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s19",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "The most important factor in our environment is the state of our own minds.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 132.44,
      "endTime": 139.01,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s20",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "It is well known that where the white man has invaded a primitive culture,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 139.02,
      "endTime": 144.01,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "It",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "它"
          },
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          },
          {
            "word": "Well",
            "pos": "adj.",
            "meaning": "健康的，良好的"
          },
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          },
          {
            "word": "White",
            "pos": "adj.",
            "meaning": "白色的"
          },
          {
            "word": "Man",
            "pos": "n.",
            "meaning": "男人"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s21",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "the most destructive effects have come not from physical weapons but from ideas.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 144.02,
      "endTime": 151.34,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Not",
            "pos": "adv.",
            "meaning": "不，不是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s22",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "Ideas are dangerous.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 151.35,
      "endTime": 154.28,
      "analysis": {
        "words": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s23",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "The Holy Office knew this full well when it caused heretics to be burned in days gone by.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 154.29,
      "endTime": 161.1,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "This",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "这，这个"
          },
          {
            "word": "Well",
            "pos": "adj.",
            "meaning": "健康的，良好的"
          },
          {
            "word": "It",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "它"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s24",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "Indeed, the concept of free speech only exists in our modern society because when you are inside a community,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 161.11,
      "endTime": 170.22,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "You",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "你，你们"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s25",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "you are conditioned by the conventions of the community to such a degree that it is very difficult to conceive of anything really destructive.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 170.23,
      "endTime": 180.75,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "You",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "你，你们"
          },
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          },
          {
            "word": "It",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "它"
          },
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          },
          {
            "word": "Very",
            "pos": "adv.",
            "meaning": "很，非常"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s26",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "It is only someone looking on from outside that can inject the dangerous thoughts.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 180.76,
      "endTime": 187.34,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "It",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "它"
          },
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          },
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s27",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "I do not doubt that it would be possible to inject ideas into the modern world that would utterly destroy us.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 187.35,
      "endTime": 195.03,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Not",
            "pos": "adv.",
            "meaning": "不，不是"
          },
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          },
          {
            "word": "It",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "它"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s28",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "I would like to give you an example, but fortunately I cannot do so.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 195.04,
      "endTime": 201.16,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "You",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "你，你们"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s29",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "Perhaps it will suffice to mention the nuclear bomb.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 201.17,
      "endTime": 205.21,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "It",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "它"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s30",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "Imagine the effect on a reasonably advanced technological society,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 205.22,
      "endTime": 210.99
    },
    {
      "id": "s31",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "one that still does not possess the bomb, of making it aware of the possibility, of supplying suffcient details to enable the thing to be constructed.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 211,
      "endTime": 222.1,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          },
          {
            "word": "Not",
            "pos": "adv.",
            "meaning": "不，不是"
          },
          {
            "word": "It",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "它"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s32",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "20 or 30 pages of information handed to any of the major world powers around the year 1925,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 222.11,
      "endTime": 230.05
    },
    {
      "id": "s33",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "would have been sufficient to change the course of world history.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 230.06,
      "endTime": 234.73
    },
    {
      "id": "s34",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "It is a strange thought, but I believe a correct one,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 234.74,
      "endTime": 239.39,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "It",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "它"
          },
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s35",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "that twenty or thirty pages of ideas and information would be capable of turning the present-day world upside down, or even destroying it.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 239.4,
      "endTime": 252.65,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          },
          {
            "word": "It",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "它"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s36",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "I have often tried to conceive of what those pages might contain,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 252.66,
      "endTime": 258.17,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "What",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "什么"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s37",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "but of course I cannot do so because I am a prisoner of the present-day world, just as all of you are.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 258.18,
      "endTime": 266.8,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "You",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "你，你们"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s38",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "We cannot think outside the particular patterns that our brains are conditioned to, or,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 266.81,
      "endTime": 273.86,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s39",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "to be more accurate we can think only a very little way outside and then only if we are very original.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 273.87,
      "endTime": 278.87,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Very",
            "pos": "adv.",
            "meaning": "很，非常"
          }
        ]
      }
    }
  ]
